@startuml
title State diagram for the BPO Management System

[*] --> InitialState

state "Initial State" as InitialState
InitialState : entry / start state

state "Filter by Category" as FilterCategory
FilterCategory : entry / user selects category filter
FilterCategory : do / search by category
FilterCategory : exit / display matching users

state "Filter by Price Range" as FilterPriceRange
FilterPriceRange : entry / user selects price range filter
FilterPriceRange : do / search by price range
FilterPriceRange : exit / display matching users

state "Display Matching Users" as DisplayUsers
DisplayUsers : entry / users are displayed based on chosen criteria
DisplayUsers : exit / users are shown

InitialState --> FilterCategory : Select Category Filter
InitialState --> FilterPriceRange : Select Price Range Filter

FilterCategory --> DisplayUsers
FilterPriceRange --> DisplayUsers

DisplayUsers --> InitialState : Back to Initial State

@enduml
